WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:40.570
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.289 --> 01:43.700
[Episode 37]

01:45.710 --> 01:47.000
When I was young,

01:49.070 --> 01:51.930
I also had a friend
who shared life and death with me.

01:53.870 --> 01:54.729
Where is he now?

01:56.759 --> 01:58.560
I haven't seen him in a long time.

02:00.230 --> 02:01.760
He might have died long ago.

02:02.760 --> 02:03.480
Or perhaps,

02:05.230 --> 02:07.230
just like in this play,

02:08.280 --> 02:09.740
he has forgotten about me.

02:12.280 --> 02:13.150
I see.

03:12.120 --> 03:12.780
Don't move.

03:14.520 --> 03:16.520
Be careful not to reopen your wound.

03:18.750 --> 03:20.079
What exactly happened?

03:20.750 --> 03:21.880
You are still alive?

03:22.190 --> 03:23.310
Have you forgotten?

03:23.310 --> 03:24.310
I am a cultivator,

03:24.710 --> 03:26.400
so naturally I have a magical artifact
to protect myself.

03:26.400 --> 03:27.960
Although that girl's sword aura
was fierce,

03:27.960 --> 03:29.690
it only made me bleed and faint.

03:30.240 --> 03:31.970
It didn't hit any vital organs.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.780
What about the others?

03:37.240 --> 03:38.640
Are there any survivors?

03:39.150 --> 03:40.030
When I woke up,

03:40.750 --> 03:42.079
they were already dead.

03:43.710 --> 03:44.800
Do you still have any strength?

03:44.800 --> 03:46.329
We must leave here quickly.

03:46.960 --> 03:50.280
The people from the Central Plains
immortal sects are still in the city?

03:50.280 --> 03:52.090
They are not from
the Central Plains immortal sects.

03:52.090 --> 03:52.910
The cultivators from the Central Plains

03:52.910 --> 03:53.640
are all pawns

03:53.870 --> 03:55.800
in someone's scheme, just like us.

03:56.860 --> 03:57.790
Search the area!

04:01.280 --> 04:02.740
Let's go! They are coming.

04:05.750 --> 04:06.880
Go check over there!

04:07.430 --> 04:08.230
Open the door!

04:08.470 --> 04:09.270
Open the door!

04:09.280 --> 04:10.080
Open the door!

04:10.280 --> 04:10.870
Hurry up!

04:11.000 --> 04:11.800
Open the door!

04:24.560 --> 04:25.820
Zhanying, be careful.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.159
You go first!

04:51.230 --> 04:52.490
We can't both die here!

04:53.159 --> 04:53.760
Zhanying!

05:12.360 --> 05:13.000
Go!

05:28.430 --> 05:29.270
Take them away.

05:29.270 --> 05:29.930
-Yes!
-Yes!

05:49.560 --> 05:50.920
If you are tired, Master,

05:50.920 --> 05:52.250
please go get some rest.

05:53.310 --> 05:54.430
How could I do that?

05:54.920 --> 05:55.950
You're my guest,

05:57.159 --> 05:58.690
and you've been helping me.

05:59.100 --> 06:00.130
If I leave you here

06:00.160 --> 06:00.830
alone,

06:01.160 --> 06:03.490
wouldn't that be taking advantage of you?

06:04.160 --> 06:04.870
Besides,

06:05.510 --> 06:06.640
I like staying here.

06:07.160 --> 06:09.190
It's comfortable and quiet.

06:11.000 --> 06:12.060
You are the Master.

06:12.190 --> 06:13.390
As long as you like it,

06:13.600 --> 06:16.200
anywhere can be
a quiet and comfortable place.

06:17.240 --> 06:18.840
You are wrong about that, Lu.

06:19.830 --> 06:20.800
As the Master,

06:21.510 --> 06:23.680
I may seem to hold a high position

06:24.480 --> 06:25.800
and have many people

06:26.040 --> 06:26.900
at my disposal,

06:27.070 --> 06:27.720
but

06:28.830 --> 06:31.160
the daily chores
are quite tedious and troublesome.

06:31.160 --> 06:32.680
Every day, people come to me

06:32.680 --> 06:33.880
either with requests

06:33.950 --> 06:36.270
or asking for approval

06:36.430 --> 06:37.360
to spend money.

06:39.510 --> 06:40.710
There's no free time.

06:47.000 --> 06:47.750
Lu,

06:48.830 --> 06:50.230
do you belong to any sect?

06:54.040 --> 06:56.100
Your medical skills seem quite good.

06:56.510 --> 06:57.680
If you are willing,

06:58.430 --> 07:00.120
you can join my Qinghong Sect.

07:02.510 --> 07:03.270
Master,

07:04.480 --> 07:05.240
I have a sect

07:06.040 --> 07:06.800
and a master.

07:09.430 --> 07:10.830
Which great master is it?

07:12.750 --> 07:14.150
Her name is Duan Xianyin.

07:14.720 --> 07:16.580
She's the Master of Liubo Temple.

07:19.600 --> 07:20.600
Liubo Temple?

07:22.600 --> 07:24.330
I've never heard of this place.

07:26.430 --> 07:27.830
My master is a hermit

07:28.160 --> 07:29.720
and doesn't like to come out.

07:29.720 --> 07:30.510
It is normal

07:30.600 --> 07:32.330
that you don't know this place.

07:35.360 --> 07:36.390
Is she good to you?

07:39.600 --> 07:41.400
Before, because of my identity,

07:41.870 --> 07:43.310
I was rejected by both

07:43.310 --> 07:44.770
the War Demons and humans.

07:44.830 --> 07:46.690
Only my master didn't despise me.

07:46.980 --> 07:48.480
She brought me back to Liubo Temple

07:48.480 --> 07:49.810
and took good care of me.

07:50.360 --> 07:51.510
All my magic skills

07:51.750 --> 07:52.810
were taught by her.

07:54.310 --> 07:55.270
Your master

07:56.360 --> 07:57.600
is really good to you.

07:59.560 --> 08:01.310
The former master of Qinghong Sect,

08:01.310 --> 08:01.920
Yu Jiang,

08:02.600 --> 08:04.920
is also quite prestigious
in the Central Plains.

08:04.920 --> 08:07.270
You were his student?

08:07.720 --> 08:08.830
He's not my master.

08:12.160 --> 08:13.090
I have no master.

08:15.870 --> 08:16.830
When I was young,

08:17.360 --> 08:18.720
a vicious woman

08:19.040 --> 08:20.300
brought me to her home.

08:20.720 --> 08:22.190
She never smiled at me

08:24.000 --> 08:26.060
and didn't teach me any magic skills.

08:26.390 --> 08:28.360
She beat and scolded me all day

08:29.360 --> 08:30.760
and made me do heavy work.

08:31.390 --> 08:33.320
When I was tired,
I had to sleep on a hard bed.

08:33.320 --> 08:36.150
When I was hungry,
I ate her spoiled leftovers.

08:39.750 --> 08:40.929
One day,

08:40.960 --> 08:41.960
I left her place

08:43.270 --> 08:44.730
and joined Qinghong Sect.

08:45.610 --> 08:46.360
After leaving

08:46.360 --> 08:47.320
her place,

08:47.600 --> 08:48.960
I secretly swore

08:49.510 --> 08:50.670
to gain the power

08:51.960 --> 08:53.600
to protect myself

08:54.960 --> 08:56.620
and never be like I was before.

08:59.320 --> 09:00.240
Fortunately,

09:00.790 --> 09:02.150
the hard times are over now.

09:02.150 --> 09:02.750
Yes,

09:04.080 --> 09:05.750
the hard times are over.

09:11.550 --> 09:12.150
Master,

09:12.670 --> 09:14.400
something happened to Xin Mei.

09:37.870 --> 09:39.750
Didn't we include rootless fruit
in the prescription?

09:39.750 --> 09:41.010
Why is there no effect?

09:49.240 --> 09:50.170
Why is it so cold?

09:51.790 --> 09:52.390
Yingying,

09:52.670 --> 09:53.600
pass on my order.

09:53.790 --> 09:56.480
In the future,
use boiling water to brew the medicine.

09:56.480 --> 09:58.940
Once it has cooled to a warm temperature,

09:59.200 --> 10:00.360
give it to Miss Xin.

10:01.790 --> 10:02.320
Yes.

10:04.630 --> 10:05.790
Don't worry, Lu.

10:06.080 --> 10:08.030
Within half a month,

10:08.360 --> 10:09.960
Miss Xin will recover.

10:33.720 --> 10:34.390
Don't run!

10:47.480 --> 10:49.610
Xin Xie Manor failed to teach you well,

10:49.630 --> 10:51.000
so I will deal with you

10:51.000 --> 10:52.390
on behalf of your master.

10:52.390 --> 10:53.720
Who do you think you are?

11:13.910 --> 11:15.630
You think I can't kill you?

11:26.670 --> 11:27.530
There's no one?

11:28.150 --> 11:28.810
It's a trap!

11:31.120 --> 11:31.980
Where are they?

11:43.720 --> 11:44.360
Xu Feng!

11:45.190 --> 11:46.250
What are you doing?

11:54.720 --> 11:55.250
Retreat!

12:24.750 --> 12:25.720
I'm not playing anymore.

12:25.720 --> 12:27.180
It's boring to always win.

12:41.200 --> 12:43.130
You have been sitting here all day.

12:43.240 --> 12:45.040
Come and play with me for a while.

12:50.240 --> 12:51.120
Young man.

12:51.720 --> 12:52.630
Do you remember

12:52.960 --> 12:53.840
the deal

12:53.840 --> 12:54.910
we made before?

13:00.750 --> 13:02.550
The thing you are looking for...

13:06.390 --> 13:06.990
Miss, sir,

13:07.200 --> 13:08.730
the Master asked to see you.

13:23.080 --> 13:23.600
Master.

13:30.150 --> 13:30.880
You're here?

13:37.150 --> 13:37.960
These are...

13:40.030 --> 13:42.030
the woodblocks
of the Unparalleled Secret Magic?

13:42.030 --> 13:42.720
Yes.

13:43.360 --> 13:44.100
These

13:44.270 --> 13:45.400
are all misprinted.

13:45.630 --> 13:46.890
It was already not easy

13:47.030 --> 13:48.440
to find them.

13:54.320 --> 13:55.520
Are these all of them?

13:55.630 --> 13:56.510
Yes.

13:56.720 --> 13:58.320
And they're all misprinted.

13:59.000 --> 13:59.750
Look here.

14:00.200 --> 14:02.730
The character "white"
was carved as "right."

14:03.720 --> 14:04.390
Therefore,

14:04.790 --> 14:06.960
this woodblock is useless.

14:07.750 --> 14:08.590
And here.

14:09.240 --> 14:11.550
The spacing between these 3 lines
is too tight.

14:11.550 --> 14:12.840
Overall, it looks

14:13.270 --> 14:14.720
very uncoordinated.

14:16.360 --> 14:17.030
And here.

14:18.200 --> 14:20.080
This is Volume 5.

14:20.480 --> 14:21.680
They carved it twice,

14:22.000 --> 14:23.530
and both times it was wrong.

14:23.910 --> 14:24.750
And here.

14:25.790 --> 14:26.920
It's badly damaged,

14:27.120 --> 14:29.120
and the characters are hard to read.

14:29.150 --> 14:30.080
To restore them,

14:30.550 --> 14:31.950
it will take some effort.

15:15.790 --> 15:17.320
You've been busy all night.

15:17.550 --> 15:18.440
Talk to me.

15:18.750 --> 15:19.550
Fu Tian said

15:19.790 --> 15:20.720
there are a few more

15:20.720 --> 15:22.320
unfound woodblocks in the warehouse.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.720
Can you help me find them?

15:25.000 --> 15:26.320
Come on, Sir Lu.

15:26.960 --> 15:28.510
Are you really that idle

15:28.510 --> 15:29.550
and ignorant?

15:30.320 --> 15:31.750
I am the head of the Eight Vajras

15:31.750 --> 15:33.280
of Qinghong Sect after all.

15:33.390 --> 15:34.390
What's in it for me

15:35.390 --> 15:37.190
if you order me around like this?

15:44.200 --> 15:44.720
Here.

15:45.510 --> 15:46.320
What's this?

15:47.440 --> 15:48.240
Your benefit.

16:05.670 --> 16:06.320
This is...

16:08.360 --> 16:09.200
my hometown?

16:11.020 --> 16:13.200
You said your hometown
has seas of flowers.

16:13.200 --> 16:14.030
But there's

16:14.150 --> 16:15.720
no such place in North Xiang.

16:15.720 --> 16:16.790
There are only mountains,

16:16.790 --> 16:18.190
endless high mountains.

16:18.870 --> 16:20.570
Mountains stretch on in layers,

16:20.570 --> 16:21.690
and sand pours down

16:21.720 --> 16:22.910
like a waterfall.

16:24.150 --> 16:25.080
I know a place.

16:25.910 --> 16:27.150
Every May,

16:27.550 --> 16:29.010
thorny roses bloom there,

16:29.150 --> 16:31.280
covering the ground in a deep crimson.

16:33.240 --> 16:34.440
If you trust me,

16:35.080 --> 16:37.440
you can follow the Pansuo Ancient Trail
to look for it.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.080
Perhaps,

16:38.510 --> 16:39.370
you can find it.

16:59.480 --> 17:00.220
Lu Qianqiao.

17:01.390 --> 17:03.750
You said earlier
that you wanted the Sunblock.

17:03.750 --> 17:05.010
What do you need it for?

17:06.349 --> 17:07.680
I need it for something.

17:09.790 --> 17:10.650
Can you find it?

17:11.829 --> 17:12.680
Not now.

17:13.349 --> 17:14.550
But if I find it later,

17:15.030 --> 17:16.160
I'll bring it to you.

17:17.960 --> 17:18.480
Thanks.

17:26.079 --> 17:27.000
You'd better take Xin Mei

17:27.000 --> 17:27.859
and leave here.

17:33.000 --> 17:33.590
Why?

17:35.160 --> 17:36.510
Because the moon here

17:37.030 --> 17:38.230
isn't bright enough.

19:21.240 --> 19:22.570
Lu Zhanying's machete?

19:23.440 --> 19:24.160
Didn't they say

19:24.160 --> 19:26.000
the machete was buried in the tomb?

19:26.000 --> 19:27.030
Why is it here?

19:30.440 --> 19:31.070
Xin Mei...

20:18.350 --> 20:19.440
Did I wake you up?

20:20.830 --> 20:21.510
No.

20:23.350 --> 20:24.960
You shouldn't have drunk so much wine.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.490
It will give you a headache.

20:27.640 --> 20:28.310
Yuan.

20:30.680 --> 20:31.610
Do you miss home?

20:38.350 --> 20:38.950
Oh, right.

20:40.000 --> 20:41.080
You grew up with me

20:41.110 --> 20:42.350
in Qinghong Sect.

20:43.160 --> 20:44.360
You don't have a home.

20:53.400 --> 20:55.000
But I still remember my home.

20:58.270 --> 20:59.440
I still remember it.

21:14.310 --> 21:15.160
Lu,

21:16.030 --> 21:18.360
Gold corners, silver sides, grass belly.

21:18.440 --> 21:20.040
Judging from your Go skills,

21:20.380 --> 21:22.240
you don't seem to know how to play.

21:25.240 --> 21:26.770
Since you're so confident,

21:27.310 --> 21:28.570
why don't we make a bet?

21:29.640 --> 21:30.270
Sure.

21:30.960 --> 21:32.220
What are we betting on?

21:33.270 --> 21:35.070
You own Qinghong Sect,

21:35.400 --> 21:36.680
which has tens of thousands
of fertile fields

21:36.680 --> 21:38.270
and thousands of buildings.

21:38.270 --> 21:40.350
Half of the people in North Xiang
are your believers.

21:40.350 --> 21:41.720
You don't lack

21:42.000 --> 21:43.070
power or money.

21:44.200 --> 21:45.260
I don't have anything

21:45.260 --> 21:46.130
that you

21:46.160 --> 21:47.030
would fancy.

21:47.680 --> 21:48.340
Why don't we

21:49.000 --> 21:50.260
make a bet on an answer?

21:52.240 --> 21:53.160
What answer?

21:55.350 --> 21:56.480
You ask, I answer.

21:57.000 --> 21:58.920
No reservations, no deception.

22:00.510 --> 22:01.480
Interesting.

22:09.400 --> 22:10.930
When I started learning Go,

22:11.480 --> 22:12.680
I heard a saying.

22:13.270 --> 22:14.270
Playing Go

22:14.890 --> 22:16.620
is like a spider spinning a web.

22:16.880 --> 22:18.680
You have to carefully weave a dense net

22:18.680 --> 22:20.280
under your opponent's watch

22:20.480 --> 22:21.810
without being noticed.

22:22.790 --> 22:24.990
Until the opponent crashes into the net

22:25.160 --> 22:27.420
and realizes they've fallen into a trap.

22:28.880 --> 22:30.110
Why do you think

22:30.830 --> 22:32.110
I'm not weaving a net?

22:37.360 --> 22:38.800
I underestimated you.

22:39.350 --> 22:40.270
What question?

22:41.240 --> 22:41.880
Go ahead.

22:44.110 --> 22:44.880
Why

22:45.260 --> 22:46.130
did you build

22:46.160 --> 22:47.030
Sihe Library?

22:48.720 --> 22:50.110
I told you before.

22:50.510 --> 22:52.910
It's for the continuation of civilization

22:53.240 --> 22:55.040
and the future of the Human Race.

23:05.790 --> 23:07.000
My turn to ask.

23:08.400 --> 23:11.400
Did you travel all the way
from the Central Plains

23:12.160 --> 23:13.510
just to escort

23:14.000 --> 23:15.790
the people of Wushuang Society

23:16.400 --> 23:18.400
to copy and borrow books?

23:19.400 --> 23:19.960
No.

23:20.990 --> 23:22.650
I came here for my own business

23:22.830 --> 23:24.510
and to visit my master.

23:26.720 --> 23:29.920
Is it for the Master of Liubo Temple?

23:31.400 --> 23:33.000
That's the second question.

23:34.680 --> 23:35.310
Okay.

23:42.070 --> 23:44.070
Since Sihe Library is so important,

23:44.640 --> 23:46.000
why didn't a single person

23:46.000 --> 23:47.550
from Qinghong Sect appear

23:48.110 --> 23:48.880
when the fire burned

23:48.880 --> 23:50.110
for half a day?

23:51.590 --> 23:52.440
That day,

23:52.830 --> 23:55.440
you had a conflict with the people
from the immortal sects,

23:55.440 --> 23:57.790
which caused chaos
among the civilians in the city.

23:57.790 --> 23:59.120
The roads were crowded,

23:59.400 --> 24:01.000
and there was no way forward.

24:14.040 --> 24:15.520
You've been

24:15.550 --> 24:16.680
in the Central Plains for so many years.

24:16.680 --> 24:19.640
Have you contacted your master?

24:21.160 --> 24:21.880
No.

24:29.000 --> 24:30.200
If it's so important,

24:30.550 --> 24:32.350
why was there no one guarding it?

24:33.170 --> 24:34.590
Even if there had been
just one capable Vajra

24:34.590 --> 24:35.720
like Zuo Yingying,

24:36.070 --> 24:36.750
it wouldn't have

24:36.750 --> 24:37.810
ended up like this.

24:40.160 --> 24:41.820
I told you this a long time ago.

24:42.310 --> 24:43.790
Half of the people in North Xiang

24:43.790 --> 24:46.510
are followers of our Qinghong Sect.

24:48.200 --> 24:50.310
There was no need for defenses.

25:01.960 --> 25:04.690
No defenses,
but there's a restriction on entry.

25:05.400 --> 25:06.860
It opens once every 5 years

25:07.200 --> 25:09.200
and stays open for only 10 days each time.

25:09.200 --> 25:10.440
Without exchanging

25:10.440 --> 25:11.790
calligraphy, painting,
or books of equal value,

25:11.790 --> 25:12.790
one cannot enter.

25:13.590 --> 25:14.960
Once inside, you can only view,

25:14.960 --> 25:15.750
not copy.

25:16.440 --> 25:17.110
Why is that?

25:18.480 --> 25:20.410
If one sincerely seeks something,

25:20.480 --> 25:21.920
let alone such rules,

25:23.030 --> 25:25.030
even if it meant going through hell,

25:25.310 --> 25:26.570
they would still come.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.380
Sihe Library was burned down.

25:38.440 --> 25:39.440
And Qinghong Sect

25:39.750 --> 25:41.070
just let those from the immortal sects go

25:41.070 --> 25:41.880
so easily?

25:43.740 --> 25:45.880
The immortal sects in the Central Plains
are intricately connected

25:45.880 --> 25:47.210
and rely on one another.

25:47.350 --> 25:48.680
Qinghong Sect is weak

25:49.350 --> 25:51.510
and simply unable to stand up to them.

25:59.240 --> 26:00.700
Unable to stand up to them?

26:03.880 --> 26:04.940
It seems that today

26:05.200 --> 26:07.260
we won't be able to decide the winner.

26:10.680 --> 26:11.740
It doesn't matter.

26:12.070 --> 26:13.350
There's plenty of time.

26:13.350 --> 26:14.080
There will be

26:14.550 --> 26:16.750
plenty of opportunities in the future.

26:44.920 --> 26:46.790
Buried here is a girl.

26:47.110 --> 26:48.110
She was in her 20s,

26:48.510 --> 26:50.400
looked quite pretty.

26:50.720 --> 26:51.960
She used a machete.

26:52.830 --> 26:55.230
She was buried together with this machete.

26:56.400 --> 26:58.260
I just feel a connection with you.

26:59.200 --> 27:00.800
I want to be friends with you.

27:02.350 --> 27:03.610
Even if I am a War Demon?

27:04.110 --> 27:05.570
Even if you are a War Demon.

27:06.720 --> 27:07.550
You'd better take Xin Mei

27:07.550 --> 27:08.750
and leave this place.

27:09.510 --> 27:10.750
Because the moon here

27:11.440 --> 27:12.640
isn't bright enough.

29:18.200 --> 29:20.260
Her immortal perception was dug out.

29:42.270 --> 29:43.200
Lu?

29:44.110 --> 29:45.550
Did you get lost

29:45.640 --> 29:47.440
or accidentally break in?

29:50.000 --> 29:52.660
You're hunting
the immortal sect cultivators.

29:53.750 --> 29:54.350
What?

29:55.030 --> 29:56.070
You found out?

29:57.610 --> 29:59.000
So people from the immortal sect
are allowed

29:59.000 --> 30:00.480
to burn my Sihe Library

30:00.880 --> 30:02.210
and slaughter mortals,

30:02.350 --> 30:03.810
while I cannot fight back?

30:04.160 --> 30:05.400
Must we be like meat

30:05.550 --> 30:07.550
on a chopping block

30:08.110 --> 30:09.370
for them to slaughter?

30:09.550 --> 30:11.880
But Lu Zhanying
is from the Wushuang Society.

30:11.880 --> 30:13.680
If you stand with the Human Race,

30:14.000 --> 30:15.730
you shouldn't have killed her.

30:17.510 --> 30:18.640
Those not of our kind

30:19.270 --> 30:21.400
are sure to have different loyalties.

30:22.400 --> 30:24.270
She already had immortal perception.

30:24.270 --> 30:26.030
Today she's in the Wushuang Society,

30:26.030 --> 30:27.290
but tomorrow she might

30:27.480 --> 30:29.240
defect to the immortal sects.

30:32.360 --> 30:33.560
Isn't Qinghong Sect

30:33.720 --> 30:34.790
an immortal sect?

30:35.200 --> 30:36.350
Qinghong Sect

30:38.240 --> 30:39.590
is different from them.

30:40.920 --> 30:41.640
Different?

30:43.110 --> 30:44.640
If there's any difference,

30:44.720 --> 30:47.030
it's that you are better
at disguising yourself.

30:47.030 --> 30:49.070
First, you used
the Unparalleled Secret Magic as bait

30:49.070 --> 30:51.000
to lure the Wushuang Society here.

30:51.070 --> 30:53.110
Then you used the Wushuang Society as bait

30:53.110 --> 30:54.910
to lure the immortal sects here.

30:55.000 --> 30:56.920
What a classic move of
"the mantis stalks the cicada,

30:56.920 --> 30:58.650
unaware of the oriole behind."

31:15.510 --> 31:16.770
If my guess is correct,

31:17.920 --> 31:18.880
you did all this

31:19.240 --> 31:20.750
to seize immortal perception.

31:20.750 --> 31:21.350
But why

31:21.350 --> 31:22.560
did you leave me and Xin Mei

31:22.560 --> 31:23.890
alone in the paper mill?

31:25.240 --> 31:26.640
What was your intention?

31:29.270 --> 31:30.590
I did hide

31:30.590 --> 31:31.790
some things from you.

31:32.400 --> 31:33.600
But there is one thing

31:34.750 --> 31:35.810
I didn't lie about.

31:38.350 --> 31:39.270
Lu Qianqiao,

31:40.800 --> 31:41.690
I really want

31:41.720 --> 31:42.790
to be your friend.

31:47.920 --> 31:49.680
You want to be my friend?

31:52.830 --> 31:54.200
You're full of lies!

32:12.550 --> 32:13.610
Watch out, Master!

32:21.920 --> 32:22.720
Find him.

32:24.030 --> 32:24.550
Yes.

32:42.400 --> 32:43.070
Xin Mei!

32:49.440 --> 32:50.510
Search carefully.

32:50.510 --> 32:51.070
Yes!

32:53.160 --> 32:53.750
Lu!

32:55.450 --> 32:56.350
Why are you here?

32:56.350 --> 32:57.080
Come with me!

32:57.400 --> 32:58.350
Xin Mei is missing.

32:58.350 --> 32:59.070
There's no time.

32:59.070 --> 32:59.930
Let's go first.

33:28.440 --> 33:29.000
Sheng!

33:29.350 --> 33:30.240
You're back!

33:34.000 --> 33:34.800
What's wrong?

33:36.070 --> 33:36.730
Miss Sheng.

33:37.270 --> 33:38.200
You're injured?

33:38.350 --> 33:39.280
Are you alright?

33:39.310 --> 33:40.970
I'm fine. It's just a scratch.

33:41.160 --> 33:42.020
What about you?

33:42.200 --> 33:43.260
How did you get out?

33:43.410 --> 33:44.830
After you lured those people away,

33:44.830 --> 33:46.000
we followed your instructions

33:46.000 --> 33:47.030
and slipped out through the back door,

33:47.030 --> 33:48.160
taking a small path into the woods

33:48.160 --> 33:49.790
before reaching the official road.

33:49.790 --> 33:51.190
Did anyone else find you?

33:51.720 --> 33:53.030
There should be more than one group
chasing you.

33:53.030 --> 33:53.510
Yes.

33:53.920 --> 33:55.640
There were a few people
from the immortal sects.

33:55.640 --> 33:57.440
We couldn't fight them off at first,

33:57.440 --> 33:59.840
but luckily a righteous warrior helped us.

33:59.880 --> 34:01.200
It was a one-armed man.

34:01.960 --> 34:03.110
A one-armed man?

34:03.680 --> 34:04.160
Yes.

34:04.680 --> 34:06.340
They knew each other, I think.

34:06.480 --> 34:07.710
Because the girl from the immortal sects

34:07.710 --> 34:08.510
was very surprised

34:08.510 --> 34:09.400
to see him.

34:09.540 --> 34:10.949
That man was awesome.

34:11.150 --> 34:12.920
He beat them back
in just a couple of moves.

34:12.920 --> 34:13.520
Oh, right.

34:13.570 --> 34:14.770
He also left us a horse

34:14.800 --> 34:16.000
and some dry rations.

34:16.630 --> 34:17.290
Where is he?

34:17.400 --> 34:18.110
He left.

34:20.030 --> 34:21.280
It's a bit dangerous here.

34:21.280 --> 34:22.070
Let's go too.

34:36.280 --> 34:37.480
How are you doing now?

34:38.920 --> 34:39.920
I won't die.

34:40.659 --> 34:41.520
How did you know

34:41.550 --> 34:43.320
there was something wrong
with the master of Qinghong Sect?

34:43.320 --> 34:44.449
I received a letter.

34:45.000 --> 34:46.460
It said you fell into a trap

34:46.510 --> 34:47.770
and told me to save you.

34:48.840 --> 34:50.040
Who wrote the letter?

34:50.440 --> 34:51.170
I don't know.

34:52.960 --> 34:54.219
You're badly injured.

34:54.440 --> 34:55.770
Where are we going next?

34:56.920 --> 34:57.850
To Liubo Temple.

34:59.480 --> 35:00.280
Liubo Temple?

35:01.550 --> 35:03.480
Xin Mei is in their hands right now.

35:03.710 --> 35:05.230
Qinghong Sect has many people.

35:05.230 --> 35:06.000
Just the two of us

35:06.000 --> 35:07.230
are no match for them.

35:08.400 --> 35:09.730
Let's go to Liubo Temple

35:09.800 --> 35:10.860
and find my master.

35:11.880 --> 35:12.410
Let's go.

35:32.070 --> 35:32.800
Xin Mei.

35:33.670 --> 35:34.320
Xin Mei.

35:36.190 --> 35:37.000
Xin Mei.

35:38.070 --> 35:38.840
Xin Mei.

35:41.110 --> 35:41.840
Xin Mei.

35:47.190 --> 35:47.840
Xin Mei.

35:50.880 --> 35:52.010
Lord of Rust-Sword?

35:52.510 --> 35:53.440
Thank goodness.

35:53.710 --> 35:54.970
You're finally awake.

35:55.480 --> 35:56.410
Why are you here?

35:56.760 --> 35:58.510
I wanted to ask you the same thing.

35:58.510 --> 35:59.000
Ever since

35:59.000 --> 36:00.630
you were locked up here yesterday,

36:00.630 --> 36:01.820
I kept calling out to you all night,

36:01.820 --> 36:02.710
but you never woke up.

36:02.710 --> 36:04.040
I thought you were dead.

36:04.800 --> 36:05.730
Where are we now?

36:08.280 --> 36:09.140
Qinghong Sect.

36:09.480 --> 36:10.740
When I woke up that day,

36:11.030 --> 36:12.490
you two were already gone.

36:47.190 --> 36:48.520
Xia Xuanzi was dead too.

36:49.800 --> 36:51.110
I was severely injured

36:51.550 --> 36:53.010
and couldn't move easily.

36:53.400 --> 36:55.670
So I thought
I could sneak into Phoenix City

36:55.670 --> 36:56.760
to heal

36:57.840 --> 36:59.440
while asking around for you.

37:02.110 --> 37:03.510
My injuries were too severe,

37:03.510 --> 37:05.110
so I ran out of strength and passed out.

37:05.110 --> 37:05.920
When I woke up,

37:06.190 --> 37:08.030
it was Zhanying who was taking care of me.

37:08.030 --> 37:08.800
Zhanying?

37:09.320 --> 37:10.380
She is still alive?

37:12.320 --> 37:14.400
That day, Jiang Ji's sword
missed by a cun,

37:14.400 --> 37:16.030
so it didn't hurt her heart meridian.

37:16.030 --> 37:17.920
She had a divine artifact
to protect herself,

37:17.920 --> 37:19.780
so she was in better shape than me.

37:20.030 --> 37:21.090
After we reunited,

37:21.480 --> 37:22.410
Zhanying told me

37:23.230 --> 37:24.340
that the entire Sihe Library

37:24.340 --> 37:25.490
was just a Go game.

37:26.070 --> 37:26.670
We,

37:27.230 --> 37:28.490
the Wushuang Society,

37:28.840 --> 37:30.670
and those immortal sects
in the Central Plains

37:30.670 --> 37:32.470
are all pawns on the chessboard.

37:35.150 --> 37:36.210
Zhanying Ying said

37:36.230 --> 37:37.000
after we

37:37.030 --> 37:38.760
evacuated from Sihe Library that day,

37:38.760 --> 37:40.800
many people from Qinghong Sect went there.

37:40.800 --> 37:42.810
They brought
all the immortal sect disciples

37:42.810 --> 37:43.850
back here

37:43.880 --> 37:45.140
as if selecting goods.

37:45.590 --> 37:46.920
We were discovered

37:47.880 --> 37:48.840
and hunted down.

37:56.050 --> 37:57.630
After we broke out of the siege,

37:57.630 --> 37:58.490
we ran far away—

37:59.230 --> 38:00.320
from Phoenix City

38:00.920 --> 38:02.320
all the way to the desert.

38:02.840 --> 38:05.300
But they still caught us
and brought us back.

38:05.800 --> 38:06.440
Then,

38:08.360 --> 38:09.620
they killed Zhanying.

38:09.960 --> 38:10.670
What?

38:11.800 --> 38:12.360
Why?

38:13.630 --> 38:14.440
I don't know.

38:15.280 --> 38:16.070
Did you see

38:16.070 --> 38:17.870
Zhanying die with your own eyes?

38:18.030 --> 38:18.590
No.

38:19.030 --> 38:20.110
They took her away.

38:20.800 --> 38:22.260
I asked about her every day.

38:22.260 --> 38:23.860
The guards found me annoying

38:24.550 --> 38:26.350
and told me she was already dead.

38:27.770 --> 38:28.920
They said no cultivator

38:28.920 --> 38:30.650
can leave Qinghong Sect alive.

38:32.750 --> 38:33.610
What about you?

38:34.000 --> 38:35.660
Why were you brought here too?

38:35.880 --> 38:37.080
Where is Lu Qianqiao?

38:37.590 --> 38:38.480
I don't know.

38:39.150 --> 38:40.030
That day, after Xia Xuanzi

38:40.030 --> 38:40.840
knocked me out,

38:40.840 --> 38:42.240
I remained unconscious.

38:42.800 --> 38:43.920
I only vaguely

38:43.940 --> 38:45.030
heard some sounds.

38:45.590 --> 38:46.920
We must have been saved,

38:47.710 --> 38:48.960
but I have no idea

38:49.070 --> 38:50.330
what exactly happened

38:50.470 --> 38:51.330
or why I'm here.

38:52.230 --> 38:53.090
Lu Qianqiao...

38:54.230 --> 38:55.400
I can try to find him.

39:07.320 --> 39:08.320
Our nine apertures were sealed

39:08.320 --> 39:09.630
by the Nine Breaths Technique.

39:09.630 --> 39:11.070
I can't use my martial arts,

39:11.070 --> 39:13.070
and your spells aren't working either.

39:13.070 --> 39:14.470
Don't waste your energy.

39:48.840 --> 39:49.970
That is Shumen Pass.

39:50.320 --> 39:51.360
Once we cross there,

39:51.360 --> 39:53.420
we'll soon reach the Central Plains.

39:58.000 --> 39:59.070
I wonder

39:59.230 --> 40:00.440
how Master is doing.

40:02.110 --> 40:02.670
They

40:03.920 --> 40:04.650
will be fine.

40:05.960 --> 40:06.590
I believe

40:07.030 --> 40:08.590
we will definitely meet again.

40:08.590 --> 40:09.850
Fate takes many forms,

40:10.070 --> 40:12.270
but it never strays from the principle.

40:12.280 --> 40:14.630
Fate takes many forms,
but it never strays from the principle?

40:14.630 --> 40:15.700
Who taught you that?

40:15.700 --> 40:17.180
The one-armed man said it.

40:20.360 --> 40:21.760
There are people coming.

40:29.480 --> 40:31.980
[General Qin]

40:32.630 --> 40:33.400
General Qin,

40:33.840 --> 40:34.770
you really came.

40:34.880 --> 40:35.900
Upon receiving your letter,

40:35.900 --> 40:36.760
I immediately rushed here

40:36.760 --> 40:37.840
with my men overnight.

40:37.840 --> 40:39.360
It concerns the life and death
of the Human Race.

40:39.360 --> 40:40.490
How could I not come?

40:41.510 --> 40:42.570
That is Miss Sheng.

40:42.840 --> 40:43.920
Although she's a cultivator,

40:43.920 --> 40:44.960
she has a chivalrous heart

40:44.960 --> 40:46.760
and escorted us all the way here.

40:47.400 --> 40:48.660
Thank you, Miss Sheng.

40:49.190 --> 40:49.880
Miss Sheng,

40:50.000 --> 40:50.860
we are leaving.

40:50.890 --> 40:52.070
General Qin will take us

40:52.070 --> 40:52.960
to a safe place.

40:53.110 --> 40:53.840
You go ahead.

40:54.110 --> 40:55.170
I have things to do.

40:56.440 --> 40:56.960
Sheng!

40:57.460 --> 40:59.120
Aren't you going back with us?

40:59.230 --> 41:00.760
What if you run into danger?

41:23.190 --> 41:23.760
Kneel!

41:26.480 --> 41:27.150
Master.

41:27.710 --> 41:28.670
We split into 2 groups

41:28.670 --> 41:30.270
to pursue those human pills.

41:30.480 --> 41:32.000
With the two protectors holding the fort,

41:32.000 --> 41:34.440
all the Sun Moon Cavern disciples
have been captured.

41:34.440 --> 41:36.230
A few disciples of Lingji Mountain
and Tianyuan Sect

41:36.230 --> 41:37.840
are still on the run.

41:38.190 --> 41:39.280
I have had our men continue the pursuit.
